Comment: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:05.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ジパングナンバー1武芸者を目指して旅に出たムサシは、刀鍛冶コテツに弟子入りを果たし、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:05.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지팡구 제일의 무예가를 꿈꾸며 여행을 떠난 무사시는 칼 장인 코테츠에게 인정받아
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:05.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,On the journey to be the number one martial artist of Jipangu, from the master sword craftsman Kotetsu,
Comment: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ついに名刀を手にすることができたのである。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,결국엔 명검을 손에 넣게 되었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi managed to get the excellent swords at last.
Comment: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:17.97,Default,ja,0,0,0,,大満足。気分はジパングナンバー1であったが、果たして行く手に待つは風か嵐か。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:17.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,대만족, 기분은 지팡구 제일이었지만, 과연 앞길에서 기다리는 것은 바람인가 폭풍인가?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:13.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,He was very satisfied! He felt like he already became the number one of Jipangu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:17.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,but what will be waiting in front of him? Wind or storm?
Comment: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,ja,0,0,200,,おいらは師匠だ。エライだス
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,ko,0,0,200,,나는 스승이오
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,ko,0,0,80,,훌륭하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,en,0,0,200,,I am a Master
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,en,0,0,80,,Excellent!
Comment: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,船が出るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,배 출발합니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ship is about to depart!
Comment: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おい！船が出るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어이! 배 출발합니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Repeat! Shop is about to depart!
Comment: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,待った！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait!
Comment: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,その船、待った！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잠시 기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,Just a moment!
Comment: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらも乗るだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나도 타겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll ride too-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:44.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,セーフでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:44.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,세이프이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:44.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Safe-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何しろ武芸で鍛えてあるからして、これしきの事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여하튼 무예를 단련하고 있으니 이쯤이야!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Anyway, since I'm training martial arts, so this is nothing!
Comment: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん！無様な。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥! 꼴사나워라.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph! How unsightly.
Comment: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:52.89,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:52.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐라?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:52.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ！そのコジロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 저건 코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:04.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん、何が武芸で鍛えただ。アヒルの踊りみたいな見苦しい恰好をして！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:04.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥, 뭐가 무예의 단련이냐? 오리가 춤추는 것만 같은 흉한 꼴을 하고!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:04.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hah, you call that training for martial arts? You look very unsightly, like a dancing duck!
Comment: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.50,Default,ja,0,0,0,,アヒルの踊り？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오리가 춤춘다?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dancing duck?
Comment: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:08.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,違いねぇや！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:08.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,맞는 말이군!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:08.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's right!
Comment: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:14.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おのれ、よくもおいらを侮辱したでてござるとするだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:14.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네이놈, 잘도 나를 모욕했겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:14.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,How dare you bastard insult me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:18.72,Default,ja,0,0,0,,許さんだス！いざ、尋常に勝負するだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:18.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,용서할 수 없소! 자, 순순히 승부를 보시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:18.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unforgivable-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Tamely do a fair match with me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:23.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、何とか刀らしいものを手に入れたようだが。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:23.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오, 뭔가 칼다워 보이는 것을 손에 넣은 모양이구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:23.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, I see you got something that does look like a sword.
Comment: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:28.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,時場所を選ばず刀を抜くとは、まだまだ修行が足らんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:28.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,때와 장소를 가리지 못하고 칼을 뽑는 것은 아직 수련이 부족하구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:28.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see your training wasn't enough to identify where to draw your sword out and where not to!
Comment: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:33.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ほかの客の方々の迷惑も考えぬとは身の程知らずのいいところ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:33.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다른 승객 여러분에게 끼치는 폐는 생각하지 못하다니, 제 분수를 알아야지!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:33.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Can't you think about the trouble to other passengers? Do not forget who you are!
Comment: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しかしその刀、まさかおもちゃではあるまいが。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,근데 그 칼, 설마 장난감 아니냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,But I wonder... isn't that sword a toy?
Comment: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:42.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ば、馬鹿な！これは{???}かの有名な刀鍛冶コテツが鍛えた名刀でござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:42.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무, 무슨! 이건 그 유명한 칼 장인, 코테츠가 만든 명검이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:42.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,N- no way! This is an excellent sword made by Kotetsu, the famous sword craftsman-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,勝負すれば、切れはずは分かるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,승부를 보면 날카로움을 볼 수 있을 것이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,By having a match, you will see its sharpness-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,抜け、コジロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼을 꺼내시오, 코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Pull your sword out, Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.23,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しょうのないやつだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,답이 없는 녀석이군.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a hopeless guy.
Comment: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よし、あそこでどうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋다, 저긴 어떠냐.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Okay then. Let's have a match on there.
Comment: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よかろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋소!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Comment: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:07.23,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあ、コジロー！今日こそ決着を付けるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:07.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 코지로! 오늘로 결판을 내겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:07.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now, Kojirō! I'll finish this as of today-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:08.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あら？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:08.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:08.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:13.24,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お前のようなイノシシ坊やと遊んでる暇など無かったのを忘れていたよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:13.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너같은 멧돼지같은 꼬마하고 놀고 있을 여유 따위 없다는 걸 잊어먹고 있었다!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:13.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,I forgot that I had no time to play with a baby wild boar like you!
Comment: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.92,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんだスと？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.92,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐, 뭐시라?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,What did you say-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:21.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー！卑怯です！男じゃないだス！武芸者でもねぇだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:21.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로! 비겁하오! 사내답지 않소! 무예가도 아니오!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:21.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō, you're cowardly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! You're not a man-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! You're not even a martial artist-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あれは頭を使う高度戦術、無手勝流だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이건 머리를 쓰는 고도 전술, 무수승류다!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is a intense tactic that uses brain, {\i1}Mutekatsu-ryu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.42,Note,ko,0,0,0,,(무수승류: 無手勝流, 무테카츠류. 싸우지 않고 이김)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.42,Note,en,0,0,0,,(Mutekatsu-ryu: 無手勝流. Winning without fighting)
Comment: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,自分の性格を反省しろ！ばっかめ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자신의 성격을 반성해라! 바보 놈!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Have a time to reflect on yourself! Idiot!
Comment: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,えい、うるさい、黙れ黙れだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시끄럽소! 닥치시오! 닥치시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're noisy-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Shut up! Shut up-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:39.00,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おのれ！卑怯者の{???}あっぱんたん！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:39.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네이놈, 코지로! 비겁한 자식!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:39.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kojirō! You cowardly bastard!
Comment: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、みじめでござらうだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 비참하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,I feel so miserable-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,この悔しさ、絶対に忘れないでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 분함, 절대 잊지 않겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will never forget this-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:59.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジローめ！今度会ったら十枚切りに切ってやるでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:59.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로 놈! 다시 만나면 10등분으로 베어 주겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:59.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn that Kojirō! If we meet again, I'll cut you into ten pieces-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.89,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さすが名刀。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 명검!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a great sword!
Comment: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:13.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや、お見事。素晴らしい{???}けんさわき。{???}と関心しました！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:13.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이야, 훌륭하오! 대단한 검술. 진정으로 감탄했습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:13.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's splendid! Excellent swordsmanship. I am genuinely struck with admiration.
Comment: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、いいや、それほどでもござらんだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니, 그 정도는 아니오.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm not on the level of that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや、収め方もまた型にはまって。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이야, 거두는 방법도 자세가 꼭 맞고...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Your way of taking sword in is just right too...
Comment: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:28.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わたくしはコヘイと申す駆け出しの武芸者ですが、何卒先生の弟子にして頂きたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:28.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저는 코헤라고 하는 갓 시작한 무예가로, 꼭 스승님의 제자가 되고 싶습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:28.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am a beginner martial artist named Kohē, and I want to be a student of yours.
Comment: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,弟子？先生、おいらのことだスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,제자? 스승, 나 말이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Student? With me as the teacher-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.49,Default,ja,0,0,0,,は。本日ただいまより師匠と呼ばせて頂きます。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예, 오늘 지금 당장 스승님이라고 부르겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right. I will start calling you as master from now on.
Comment: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:41.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,い、しかし、まだおいら、いやいえいえ、拙者はその修行、いえいえ、技を積む。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:41.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 그래도, 나, 아니, 소생은 저, 수련, 아니, 아니, 기술을 쌓는...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:41.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bu- but, I, yet, no, I... train... no, developing techniques...
Comment: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:46.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ご謙遜なさるところがまた一段と奥ゆかしいお人だら、尊敬いたしますぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:46.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,겸손하신 모습이 또 한층 우아하게 보이십니다. 존경합니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:46.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Your modestly makes you even more elegant. I respect you.
Comment: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや、どうも。なんだスな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니, 정말 고맙소. 이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Err, thanks. I'm grateful-dasu.
Comment: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:57.91,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあさあ。あちらに茶店が見えます。団子など頂きながら大先生のお話を伺いたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:57.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 자, 저기에 찻집이 보입니다. 단고라도 드실 동안 대선생의 말씀을 생각하고 싶습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:57.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see a tea house over there. I want to think about your teachings while you have some dangos.
Comment: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:58.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,団子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:58.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,단고?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:58.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dango?!
Comment: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:08.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,仕方がないだス。団子に免じて、いやいや、おぬしの熱意に免じてお話してやるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:08.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어, 어쩔 수가 없소. 단고에는 눈이 돌아, 아니아니, 네 열의에 눈이 돌았으니 이야기를 하겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:08.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,I can't refuse that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. I have no eyes for dango, no, for your enthusiasm, so I'll talk with you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:16.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや、さすがに大先生！だんごの食べ方も実に男らしく豪快でござるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:16.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이야, 역시 대선생! 단고를 먹는 방법도 참으로 사내답게 호쾌하시군요.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:16.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's my master! The way you eat dangos is so manly and superb.
Comment: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:22.62,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん、武芸者{???}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:22.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,응, 무예가라면 먹을 때에도 사양하면 안 되오.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:22.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Righ{\alphaa0}t{\alpha0}, i{\alphaa0}f{\alpha0} you a{\alphaa0}re{\alpha0} a {\alphaa0}s{\alpha0}wo{\alphaa0}rd{\alpha0}s{\alphaa0}m{\alpha0}an, e{\alphaa0}ve{\alpha0}n w{\alphaa0}h{\alpha0}en you ea{\alphaa0}t{\alpha0}, you mu{\alphaa0}st n{\alpha0}o{\alpha0}t {\alphaa0}b{\alpha0}e mo{\alphaa0}d{\alpha0}es{\alphaa0}t{\alpha0}.
Comment: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なるほど。立派な心構えで。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇군요. 훌륭한 마음으로...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see. With a excellent spirit...
Comment: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.49,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あの、わたくしの分もよろしければどうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저, 제 몫도 원하신다면... 드세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,If you want mine too, you can have them.
Comment: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:34.36,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんだス。食べ物を残すようでは一流の武芸者にはなれんでござるだスよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:34.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔가, 먹을 것을 남겨서는 일류의 무예가가 되지 못하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:34.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,If you leave your food, you won't become a first-class martial artist-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや！満腹、満腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이야! 배불렀소.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,I feel so full.
Comment: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おやじ！いくらだスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,주인장! 얼마이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Owner! How much are they-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,へい、百問で。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네, 100문입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,They are 100 mons.
Comment: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,百問？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,100문?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,100 mons?!
Comment: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.24,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなかねどこにもないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 그런 돈은 어디에도 없소...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,I have no money for that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、いいえ、先生、こういうことは弟子のわたくしにお任せをください。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 아니, 스승님, 이런 일은 제자인 제게 맡겨 주세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, master. Leave such things to me, your student-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:54.43,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おやじさん、ご苦労さん。ここに置いていくよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:54.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,주인장, 잘 먹었소. 여기 두고 갑니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:54.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,The food was excellent today. Here you go.
Comment: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,へい、まいど。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예, 감사합니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:59.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,弟子というのは便利なものだスな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:59.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,제자란 것은 편리한 것이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:59.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Having a student is convenient-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,でししししし。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,제자하하하...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,Studehehehehehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:04.08,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,0,,{\frz50\fax-0.4\fscx110\fry-30\move(437,176,437,-100,1000,3000)\c&H202141&\3c&H7575A5&\bord5}여기서부터 쿠마노미로
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:04.08,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\frz50\fax-0.4\fscx110\fry-30\move(437,176,437,-100,1000,3000)\c&H202141&\3c&H7575A5&\bord5}Kumanomiro from here
Comment: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ジパング武芸大会。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지팡구 무예 대회인가.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jipangu Martial Arts Competition?
Comment: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:16.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい。エドトピアの将軍イエヤス公が主催するジパング1の武芸大会で、毎年年末に行われます。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:16.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예. 에도토피아의 쇼군 이에야스 공이 주최하는 지팡구 제일의 무예 대회로 매년 연말에 열립니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:16.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes. It is the most important martial arts competition of Jipangu at every year-end by Ieyasu, the shōgun of Edotopia.
Comment: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それに優勝すれば？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거기서 우승하면?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,What happens if I win?
Comment: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もちろん！ジパングナンバー1の武芸者に。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,물론! 지팡구 제일의 무예가로.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Of course you become the number one martial artist of Jipangu.
Comment: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:25.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,先生ほどの実力者なら優勝間違いないですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:25.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승님 정도의 실력이라면 우승할 것이 틀림없습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:25.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,With your level of technique, you cannot lose.
Comment: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:31.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,も、もちろんでござるだス。おいらはこれより、エドトピアに向かうだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:31.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무, 물론이오! 나는 지금부터 에도토피아를 향하겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:31.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,O- of course-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! From now on, I am heading to Edotopia-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お供いたします。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,함께 가 드리겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will go with you.
Comment: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:44.97,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おかしいな、どんどん山の中へ入っていくでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:44.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이상하오. 점점 산속에 들어가는 것 같소.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:44.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Something's not right-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. I think we're going inside to a mountain-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ？あそこに看板が言えます。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 저기에 간판이 보입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? I see a sign there.
Comment: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:53.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,無断立ち入りを禁ずる。近を犯すもの命は保障しない。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:53.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무단 출입 금지. 금령을 어긴 자의 목숨은 보장할 수 없음.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:53.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not enter. The life of violators is not guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.64,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,250)\frz24\c&H202141&\3c&H7575A5&\bord5\fs96\frx-10\fry-10}호조인
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.64,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,250)\frz24\c&H202141&\3c&H7575A5&\bord5\fs96\frx-10\fry-10}Hōzōin
Comment: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ホーゾーイン。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,호조인.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hōzōin.
Comment: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ホーゾーイン？変な名前だスな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,호조인? 이상한 이름이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hōzōin? What a weird name-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:02.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,先生、わたくし、聞いたことがあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:02.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승님, 제가 들은 바가 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:02.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master. I've heard about them.
Comment: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:09.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんでも坊さんの癖にお経はそっち抜けで、妙なやりを使う恐ろしい奴だそうです。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:09.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐래도 중 주제에 경은 제쳐두고, 묘한 창을 쓰는 무서운 놈이라 들었습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:09.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,He is a monk, but he puts the sutras away, and he is told to be using a weird spear.
Comment: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,坊さんが武芸をやるんだスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,중이 무예를 하오?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,A monk is into martial arts-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:18.50,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それだけではなく、たくさんの弟子を集めて戦争を起こし、国を倒そうと企むとの噂。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:18.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그뿐만이 아니라, 많은 제자를 모아 전쟁을 일으키고, 나라를 쓰러뜨리겠다고 계획한다고 하는 소문.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:18.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's not all. It is told that he's gathering lots of students to start a war, planning to take down the country.
Comment: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらの村のタクアン和尚ならカアアアーツっと怒るところだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내 마을에 타쿠안 스님이라면 네이놈! 하고 화낼 소리이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Takuan, a monk in my village, would shout YOU BRAT!-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:28.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,大先生の力で世のため、人のため、懲らしめてやりましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:28.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,대스승님의 힘으로 세상을 위해, 사람을 위해 응징해 줍시다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:28.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,With the master's power, let's punish them for the people and for the world!
Comment: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:33.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いうまでもないだス。こういう看板なんか壊してやるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:33.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,말할 필요도 없소. 이런 간판 따위 부수겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:33.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,No need to say-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. I will destroy such sign-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.62,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あら？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんだス？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おぬしか！ホーゾーイン大先生にケンカを売ろうってのは！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너냐! 호조인 대스승님께 시비를 거는 자는!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is it you? Did you asked for a fight to master Hōzōin?
Comment: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もしもし。このものはおいらの弟子でござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여보시오. 이 자는 내 제자이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey. This person is my student-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,話ならおいら、いや、拙者が菊でござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이야기라면 나, 아니, 소생에게 하시오.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,If you have something to say, do it to me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:07.36,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なに、お前が？冗談はそれぐらいにして、まず手をついて謝れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:07.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐냐, 네가? 농담은 그만 하고 먼저 손을 붙이고 사과해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:07.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,What, you? Stop with that joke and beg for pardon on your knees!
Comment: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:13.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,冗談っぽいだス。おいら、えらそうな奴に頭を下げるのと、{???}日々とナメクジが大嫌いだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:13.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,농담 아니오! 나는 잘난 척하는 놈에게 머리를 숙이는 것과 금가는 것과 민달팽이가 정말 싫소!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:13.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm not joking-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. I hate cracks, snails, and begging to a braggart-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ガキだと思っておとなしくすればつけやがりやって！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,애송이라 생각했지만 순순히 굴지 못할망정 싸움을 걸다니!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're not a simple brat, to ask for a fight instead of being obedient!
Comment: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.78,Default,ja,0,0,0,,痛い目にあって泣くなよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아파도 울지 마라!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't cry even if it hurts!
Comment: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:22.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,-先生！\N-おいらに任せるでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:22.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-스승님!\N-나에게 맡기시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:22.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Master!\N-Leave it to me!
Comment: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こんな連中、すぐに片づけるでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이런 패거리, 바로 처리해 주겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will take care of this bunch-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:26.43,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:26.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋소.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:26.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then.
Comment: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.54,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おのれ、{???}いわすておけば！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네이놈, 말 그만두지 못할까!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,You brat, shut your mouth!
Comment: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,構わん！ホーゾーイン流のあら切りをつけてやれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,상관없다! 호조인 류 아라기리를 보여주겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter now! I'll show you the {\i1}Aragiri{\i0} in Hōzōin flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.69,Note,ko,0,0,0,,(아라기리: 粗切り. 거칠게 대충대충 자름)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.69,Note,en,0,0,0,,({\i1}Aragiri{\i0}: 粗切り. rough cut)
Comment: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:40.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんのこれしき！こっちが稽古つけてやるでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:40.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 정도쯤이야! 내가 한 수 가르쳐 주겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:40.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is nothing! I'll teach you something instead-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.72,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うおお！やられた！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,으윽! 당했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am done for!
Comment: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,オーバーな！ただの峰打ちでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오버하긴! 그냥 칼등일 뿐이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't overact! It's just the back side of sword-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、{???}はしないことに決めているだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 무익한 일은 하지 않기로 했소!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will not do something useless-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:06.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,小僧と見て甘く見るな！取り囲んでたたきうっせるのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:06.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꼬맹이 앞에서 허둥대지 마라! 둘러싸 두들겨 죽여라!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:06.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't be flustered in front of a brat! Surround him and beat him to death!
Comment: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:12.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんの。ジパングナンバー1の武芸者を目指すムサシ様だス。簡単にはやられないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:12.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨. 지팡구 제일의 무예가를 꿈꾸는 무사시 님이오. 간단히 당하지 않소!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:12.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Musashi, working to be the number one martial artist of Jipangu-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. I won't be down so easily-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 스승님!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらから離れるでないだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나에게서 떨어지지 마시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't get away from me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい！先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네! 스승님!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right! Master!
Comment: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やるだスな、コヘイさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꽤 하는가 보오, 코헤이 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're pretty good, Kohē!
Comment: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや、偶然ですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니, 우연입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, this was by chance.
Comment: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,先生の真似をしてみただけです。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승님을 따라했을 뿐입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,I was just imitating you.
Comment: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:45.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,えい、面倒だ！本物の槍で口出しにして片づけろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:45.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,에이, 귀찮다! 진짜 창으로 찍소리 못하게 끝내버려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:45.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,They're being annoying! Finish them with real spears to make them shut up!
Comment: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,{???}おののめ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네이놈!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Comment: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.53,Default,ja,0,0,0,,先生！いけません。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승님! 안 됩니다! 여긴 달아나야 합니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, master! We have to run away from here!
Comment: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:58.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ば、馬鹿言っちゃ困るだス。おいらたち二人を、たくさんでやっつけようなんて卑怯は許せないだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:58.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 그런 말을 하면 곤란하오! 우리 둘을 여럿이 당해내겠다는 따위 비겁은 용서할 수 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:58.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,No- nonsense-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! The cowardice of many people attacking us two is unforgivable-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,先生！大丈夫ですか！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승님! 괜찮습니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master! Are you alright?!
Comment: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:15.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんの。故郷のミヤモト村では山や森でチャンバラごくを毎日やってただスからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:15.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨. 고향 미야모토 마을에서는 산이나 숲에서 칼싸움을 매일같이 해 왔으니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:15.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,No problem. I've been playing using swords even when I was in my home town Miyamoto village!
Comment: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.78,Default,ja,0,0,0,,チャンバラごくとことは大笑いだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼싸움이라니 아주 웃기는구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sword play is something to laugh about!
Comment: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.20,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それも修行の一つだス！{???}めいりもの見せるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그것도 수련의 하나이오! 명확하게 보여주겠쇼!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is definitely a training-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'll show you clearly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잡아라!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't let them run away!
Comment: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,すごい、ムサシ先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,대단해요, 무사시 스승님!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,Awesome, master Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:35.92,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こんなのちょろいだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:35.92,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이런 건 쉽소!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:35.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is nothing!
Comment: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 스승님!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ちょっと載せすぎたかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너무 부추겼나...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Maybe I pushed him too much...
Comment: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:50.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ここはどんな獣でも生きて出られぬ自然の墓場。手間が省けたわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:50.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여긴 어떤 짐승도 살아서 나갈 수 없는 자연의 무덤. 수고를 줄였군.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:50.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,You are now in the grave of nature that nobody can escape alive. One less trouble to face.
Comment: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:59.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,果たしてムサシはこのまま死んでしまうのか。疾風怒濤の後半を待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:59.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,과연 무사시는 이대로 죽고 마는가? 질풍노도의 후반을 기다려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:59.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is Musashi going to die like this? Wait for the stormy latter half!
Comment: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:13.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシさん？何見てるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:13.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 씨? 뭐 봐요?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:13.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi? What are you looking at?
Comment: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,雲だス。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,구름이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Clouds-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,구름?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Clouds?
Comment: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:19.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、今にあの雲よりもでかい男になって見せるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:19.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 지금 보이는 저 구름보다도 큰 사내가 되어 보이겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:19.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will be a man with a bigger spirit than that clouds-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ええ、きっとなれるわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네, 꼭 될 거에요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right, you will be!
Comment: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:24.56,Default,ja,0,0,0,,その時、オツルさん、
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:24.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 때가 되면 오츠루 씨,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:24.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,When that time comes, Otsuru,
Comment: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,その時は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 때?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,That time?
Comment: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:31.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,その時は。。。やわらかい手だスな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:31.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 때는... 부드러운 손이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:31.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,When that time comes... what a soft hand-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,すべすべしてるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말 얇소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,So thin-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,つるつるしてるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,매끈매끈하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,How slippery-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.23,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ちょっとひゃっこいだスが、愛してるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,조금 부끄럽지만, 사랑하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's awkward, but I love you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,オツルさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru!
Comment: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:03.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,その、た、なんだス。ここはまるで、武芸者の墓場でござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:03.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,노, 놀랐소. 뭐, 뭐, 뭣이오. 여긴 마치 무예가의 무덤같소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:03.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shocking... Wh- what is this place-{\i1}dasu{\i0}? It is like a grave for martial artists!
Comment: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,っていうことは、このおいらも。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 말은, 이 나도...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,That means, I also will...
Comment: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、死にたくないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 죽기 싫소!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't want to die-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:14.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ジパングナンバー1の武芸者になるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:14.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지팡구 제일의 무예가가 되겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:14.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,I must become the number one martial artist of Jipangu-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こんなことでくじけるおいらではないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이런 일로 꺾일 내가 아니오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will not break down by this-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.91,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おのれ、あきらめないでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 포기하지 않겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will not give up-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.24,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もういや。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,더는 싫어...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,No more...
Comment: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ここがホーゾーインの本拠地か。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}이곳이 호조인의 본거지인가.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is the stronghold of Hōzōin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:46.70,NoteOnAnimeVert,ko,0,0,0,,{\frz-70\fry-20\fs80\move(427,92,427,660)\c&H7790B2&}호조원
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:46.70,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\frz-74\fry-10\fs64\move(427,92,427,660)\c&H7790B2&}Hōzō Temple
Comment: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,果たして幕府を倒す謀反のたくらみがあるのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}과연 막부 정권을 쓰러뜨릴 반역 음모가 있는 것인가.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they planning to rebel over the shōgunate government?
Comment: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,子供の武芸者が侵入だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아이 무예가가 침입자라?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,A kid martial artist invaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:01.51,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,80,,호조인
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:01.51,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,80,,Hōzōin
Comment: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:59.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ホーゾーイン様、ご安心してください。例の岩穴に落としましたので。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:59.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,호조인 님, 안심해 주십시오. 그 바위굴에 매장하였습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:59.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Master Hōzōin. We've buried him into that cavern.
Comment: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そやつめ、一人だったのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 놈 혼자였나?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Was he alone?
Comment: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:08.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いいえ、そいつの弟子とかいう武芸者もおりましたが、これがまるっきり話になるような奴じゃありませんで、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:08.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니요, 그 녀석의 제자인가 하는 무예가도 있었지만 전혀 그랬을 리도 없고
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:08.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, there was someone who is told to be his student, but that made no sense,
Comment: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いつの間にかいなくなってしまいました。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어느 순간 없어지고 말았습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,and he disappeared unbeknownst to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.96,Note,ko,0,0,0,,{\an2\move(-54,0,104,110-)\fs40\t(0,3960,\fs32)}천하무적
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.96,Note,en,0,0,0,,{\an2\move(-54,0,104,110-)\fs40\t(0,3960,\fs32)}We are unrivaled
Comment: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.43,Default,ja,0,0,0,,{???}ネズミの一匹夜にしほおっておけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쥐새끼는 썩 꺼져라!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,Get lost, you rat!
Comment: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:24.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しかし、わが門外{???}ふっしゅのホーゾーイン流を探りに来たスパイだとすれば。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:24.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 우리 문 밖의 호조인 류를 정탐하러 온 스파이라고 하면...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:24.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,But what if it's a spy came to observe us Hōzōin family?
Comment: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.91,Default,ja,0,0,0,,探られて困るような秘密は当院にはない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알려지면 곤란한 비밀은 여기엔 없다.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,We do not have any secret that would bring us trouble.
Comment: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:31.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それより、修行の場であるこの山を荒らされては困る。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:31.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그보다도 수련의 장소에 있는 그 산이 넘보여지는 건 곤란하지.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:31.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,On the other hand, the mountain housing our training site must be kept free of invaders.
Comment: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,警備はしっかりと頼むぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,경비를 확실히 하도록!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Strengthen the defenses!
Comment: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:34.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,は！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:34.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:34.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Comment: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.49,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お願いだス。誰か助けて欲しいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오... 누군가 구해 주시오...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please... somebody save me...
Comment: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、こんなとこでは死んでも死にきれないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 이 곳에선 죽어도 미련 없이 죽지 못하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,If I die here, I wouldn't be able to die without regrets-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,腹減った。。。のどもカラカラだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,배고프오... 목도 말랐소...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,So hungry... So thirsty too-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,結局弟子も薄情なもんだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,결국 제자도 박정한 사람이오....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,That student was heartless too after all-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:02.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,でもこんなことになるなら、先生なんて粋がるんじゃなかっただス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:02.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도 이렇게 된다면 스승 따위 멋에 겨워 허세를 부리면 안 됐소...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:02.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,If I knew I was going to end like this, I shouldn't bluffed about being a master-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.72,Default,ja,0,0,0,,先生！ムサシ先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승님! 무사시 스승님!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master! Master Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.62,Default,ja,0,0,0,,これにつかまってください！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이걸 잡아 주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hold this!
Comment: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おわ！天の助け！コヘイさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,와! 하늘의 도움! 코헤이 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wah! Rescue of heaven! Kohē!
Comment: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:23.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、うまい！ありがとう、コヘイさん。おぬしはおいらの命の恩人だス。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:23.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,맛있소! 고맙소, 코헤이 씨. 너는 내 생명의 은인이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:23.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,So good! Thank you, Kohē. I owe you my life-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何おっしゃいます、先生。これも弟子の勤めです。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨 소립니까, 스승님. 이것도 제자가 애쓰는 것입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you saying, master? This is also what a student does.
Comment: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:31.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあさあ、好物の団子も用意させて頂きました。はい、どうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:31.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 좋아하시는 음식인 단고도 드십시오. 여기 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:31.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here it is. Your favorite food is dango, right?
Comment: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うまい！とってもうまいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,맛있소! 정말 맛있소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,So good! It's excellent-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:42.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,これはもち米やゴマの粉を蜂蜜などで練り固めた非常食で、栄養たっぷりの団子です。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:42.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이건 찹쌀이나 참깨를 뿌린 벌꿀 등으로 개어서 굳힌 비상식으로 영양이 듬뿍 담긴 단고입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:42.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,These are nutritious dangos made with sticky rice, sesame, and honey, which also serve as emergency rations.
Comment: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,すごいもの持ってるだスな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,대단한 걸 가지고 있소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,You have awesome things-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,先生、落ち着いて、落ち着いて！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승님, 진정하세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Calm down, master! Calm down!
Comment: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:53.36,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おかげで元気が出ただス。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:53.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,덕분에 기운이 났소.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:53.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I'm fine now-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.49,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あの寺は？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저 절은?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's that temple?
Comment: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おそらくホーゾーインの砦でございましょう。近寄らないほうが。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아마 호조인의 성일 것입니다. 가까이 가지 않는 게...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,It must be the castle of Hōzōin.
Comment: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:08.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや。乗り込んでいってひどい目に合わせてくれた荒法師どもをコテンパンにやっつけてやるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:08.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니오. 멋대로 오버하다가 날 호되게 당하게 한 승병들을 무참히 응징해 주겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:08.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,No. I will beat those ferocious monks who made me suffer black and blue.
Comment: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コヘイさん、来るだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코헤이 씨, 오시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kohē, follow me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,頼むーでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is anyone there?
Comment: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.50,Default,ja,0,0,0,,{???}号令！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Comment: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.52,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん、おぬし、昨日の小僧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라, 넌 어제 꼬맹이!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're that brat from yesterday!
Comment: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よく生きて出られたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘도 살아 나타났군!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,So you live.
Comment: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:27.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ミヤモト村のムサシは不死身でござるだス。試合で決着をばっ付けるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:27.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미야모토 마을의 무사시는 불사신이오! 시합으로 결판을 내러 왔소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:27.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi from Miyamoto village is immortal-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I am here to settle this with a match-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:28.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,面白い。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:28.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥미롭군.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:28.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Comment: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,面白い。このホーゾーインに試合を申し込むとは。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥미롭군. 이 호조인에게 시합을 요청하는 것은.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Interesting. So you ask for a match to me, Hōzōin.
Comment: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:36.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,身の程知らずもいいところ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:36.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,분수를 모르는 것도 괜찮은 일이지.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:36.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Being indiscreet is not a bad thing.
Comment: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:42.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,われこそはジパングナンバー1の武芸者を目指す、ミヤモト村のムサシでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:42.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나야말로 지팡구 제일의 무예가를 꿈꾸는 미야모토 마을의 무사시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:42.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Musashi from Miyamoto village, working to be the number one martial artist of Jipangu!
Comment: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,言って、ごしゅだんをお願いたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,단도직입적으로 시합을 부탁드리오.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,I want to ask you for a match.
Comment: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:50.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,亜流試合は禁じてあるが、わざわざ尋ねて来られたのだ。特別に許可しよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:50.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다른 유파와의 시합은 금지되어 있지만, 일부러 찾아왔겠구나. 특별히 허가해 주지.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:50.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,A match against a different school is prohibited, but I'll let you have one since you came all the way for this.
Comment: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,アメンボ！相手をしなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잔챙이! 상대해 줘라!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,You there! Contend with him!
Comment: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right!
Comment: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.02,Default,ja,0,0,0,,勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,승부!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Match!
Comment: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いざ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시작하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Let's start!
Comment: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あらら？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,参った！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,졌다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,I lost!
Comment: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,次だス！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다음!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next!
Comment: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:11.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,参った！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:11.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,졌다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:11.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,I lost!
Comment: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,次！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다음!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next!
Comment: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:27.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,えい！一人二人は面倒だス。ホーゾーイン殿と勝負するだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:27.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,에잇! 이깟 한둘은 그저 성가시오! 호조인 님과 승부를 보고 싶소!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:27.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,These ones are nothing-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I want to have a match against Hōzōin-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1728,刀をわしに向けるとはいい度胸だ。よかろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1728,칼을 내게 세우다니, 배짱 좋구나. 좋다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.51,Default,en,0,0,0,L1728,Some confidence you have, to hold your sword against me. Well then.
Comment: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:35.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1731,しかし、真剣勝負以外は受けぬが、よいかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:35.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1731,다만 진검승부 이외에는 하지 않겠다. 괜찮나?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:35.73,Default,en,0,0,0,L1731,But I do not have a match without a real sword. Will you accept?
Comment: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1736,望む所だス。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1736,바라던 바이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.19,Default,en,0,0,0,L1736,That's what I wanted-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ！先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 스승님!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! ...Master!
Comment: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,心配ないでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,걱정하지 마시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not worry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:43.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:43.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:43.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Come!
Comment: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1747,変わった槍でござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1747,희한한 창이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.51,Default,en,0,0,0,L1747,That's one strange lance-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1750,この鎌槍こそ、わがホーゾーイン流の必殺武器。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1750,이 미늘창이야말로 우리 호조인류의 필살무기!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.82,Note,en,0,0,0,L1750,({\i1}kamayari{\i0}: 鎌槍. Spear with curved cross-blades)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,This {\i1}kamayari{\i0} is the special weapon of our Hōzōin family!
Comment: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1754,いざ、勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1754,승부다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.37,Default,en,0,0,0,L1754,Begin match!
Comment: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:55.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:55.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:55.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Come!
Comment: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.60,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1812,鎌の部分を計算に入れなかっただス。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1812,쇠붙이 부분을 계산에 넣지 않았소.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.60,Default,en,0,0,0,L1812,I didn't put the metal part to my calculations-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:23.20,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1816,見たか。これぞホーゾーイン流鎌槍の特技。それだけではなく切る機能も備えた万能槍。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:23.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1816,보았나? 이게 호조인류 미늘창의 특기. 그것뿐만이 아니라 자르는 기능도 있는 만능 창.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:23.20,Default,en,0,0,0,L1816,Did you see? This is the specialty of {\i1}kamayari{\i0} of our Hōzōin family. This spear also can cut. It is capable of anything.
Comment: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.67,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1823,覚悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1823,각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.67,Default,en,0,0,0,L1823,Prepare yourself!
Comment: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.53,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1828,このままでは漬け込む隙がないでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1828,{\i1}이대로는 허점을 이용할 틈이 전혀 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.53,Default,en,0,0,0,L1828,{\i1}I cannot find a way to take advantage of anything-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.20,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1837,とどめだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1837,끝장이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.20,Default,en,0,0,0,L1837,Finishing move!
Comment: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1840,逃げるのか、小僧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1840,달아가냐, 꼬맹아!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.08,Default,en,0,0,0,L1840,Are you running away, you brat?!
Comment: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:46.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1842,違うだス。狭い道場は息が詰まるから外へ出ただけだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:46.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1842,아니오! 좁은 도장에서는 숨이 막히니까 밖으로 나왔을 뿐이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:46.63,Default,en,0,0,0,L1842,That's not it! I just came out because the air was stale inside that limited space of Dōjō!
Comment: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:49.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1847,負け惜しみだけはいっちょう前だな！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:49.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1847,패배를 인정하기 1초 전이군!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:49.63,Default,en,0,0,0,L1847,One second before you admit your loss!
Comment: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1857,うわ、動けないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1857,움직일 수가 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.37,Default,en,0,0,0,L1857,I cannot move-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1859,それ、串刺しだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1859,이랴, 꼬치 꽂기다!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.85,Default,en,0,0,0,L1859,Time for skewering!
Comment: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1903,覚悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1903,각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.42,Default,en,0,0,0,L1903,Prepare yourself!
Comment: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.52,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1909,誰だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1909,누구냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.52,Default,en,0,0,0,L1909,Who did that?!
Comment: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.43,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1914,貴様。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1914,네이놈.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.43,Default,en,0,0,0,L1914,How dare you...
Comment: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1917,うん？おぬしは。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1917,어? 너는...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.28,Default,en,0,0,0,L1917,Huh? You're...
Comment: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:23.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1920,相手はまだ少年。たってとあらば拙者がお相手いたす。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:23.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1920,상대는 아직 소년. 굳이 날뛰어야 한다면 소생이 상대하겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:23.87,Default,en,0,0,0,L1920,The opponent is a boy. If you must fight, I will content with you.
Comment: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:32.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1927,{\i1}葵の紋章。諸国を見回る警察庁長官のジュウベエ殿か。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:32.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1927,{\i1}접시꽃 문장. 제국을 돌아보는 경찰청 장관 주베 님인가...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:32.64,Default,en,0,0,0,L1927,{\i1}Emblem of hollyhock. He must be Jūbee, director of the police department who takes care of whole empire...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:38.26,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,95,,주베
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:38.26,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,95,,Jūbee
Comment: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.13,Default,ja,0,0,0,,一点の曇りもない澄んだ目だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}한 점 구름도 없는 맑은 눈이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has clear eyes without a cloud.
Comment: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何か見えましたかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무언가 보였습니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Did you see something?
Comment: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,曇りなき青空です。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,맑은 하늘입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,A clear sky.
Comment: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それを聞いて安心しました。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 말을 들으니 안심됩니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am relieved to hear that.
Comment: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:55.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,L1951,勝負を忘れたか、ホーゾーイン！覚悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:55.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,L1951,승부를 잊었소, 호조인? 각오하시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:55.37,Default,en,0,0,0,L1951,Did you forget the match-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, Hōzōin? Prepare yourself!
Comment: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もらった！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잡았소!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,I got you!
Comment: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,L2016,参った。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,L2016,졌소.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.35,Default,en,0,0,0,L2016,I lost.
Comment: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,L2017,え？どうしてでござるだス。今の勝負は相打ちでは。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,L2017,어째서오? 지금 승부는 비긴 것이...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.51,Default,en,0,0,0,L2017,Why-{\i1}dasu{\i0}? This match is a draw...
Comment: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:26.02,Default,ja,0,0,0,L2022,いやいや、自慢の槍を切れ落とされて私の負けでござる。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:26.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,L2022,아니오. 자랑스러운 창이 끊어진 제가 진 것이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:26.02,Default,en,0,0,0,L2022,No. It is my loss, as my spear has been cut off, as well as my pride.
Comment: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,L2026,以後、精進仕りまする。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,L2026,이후, 정진하겠소이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.26,Default,en,0,0,0,L2026,I will devote more, from now on.
Comment: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:29.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,L2028,ほ、本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:29.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,L2028,저, 정말이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:29.47,Default,en,0,0,0,L2028,Re- really?
Comment: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,L2029,やった！やったでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,L2029,해냈다! 해냈소!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.75,Default,en,0,0,0,L2029,I did it! I did it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:43.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,エドトピアのジパング武芸大会で改めて勝負したいでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:43.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,에도토피아의 지팡구 무예 대회에서 새롭게 다시 승부를 보고 싶소.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:43.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,I want to have a new match against you in Jipangu Martial Arts Competition in Edotopia.
Comment: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.33,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん、その折には必ず。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 바라심은 꼭.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Your wish will certainly be achieved.
Comment: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:47.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,では。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:47.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:47.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then.
Comment: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:49.60,Default,ja,0,0,0,,{???}どうちを気を付けて！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:49.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,,조심하시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:49.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take care!
Comment: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ありがとうでござるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,감사하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:58.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しかし天下一と名高いジュウベエ殿が弟子とは面白い男よ、ムサシ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:58.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}그래도 천하제일로 유명한 주베 님이 제자라니, 재미있는 소년이군. 무사시.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:58.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are an interesting boy, Musashi, to claim to have Jūbee, the unrivaled, as your student.
Comment: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、そうだ。忘れ物だス。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 참. 두고 온 것이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ah, right. You forgot something-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらが危ないとき、助けてくれたのは知ってるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내가 위험했을 때 구해 준 것은 알고 있소.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,I know that you saved me when I was in danger-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:13.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、いや、そうでしたか。あの時はもう夢中で。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:13.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아... 그랬습니까. 그 때는 몰두하다가...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:13.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh... was that so? I was kind of busy...
Comment: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:20.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、本当はあんたの先生なんかなれるうでじゃないんだス。勘弁してほしいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:20.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 사실은 당신의 스승이 될 만할 자격이 없소. 이해해 주시오.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:20.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I am not qualified to be your master-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. Please understand-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:25.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや、誤るのはわたくしです。わたくしは柳生家のジュウベエともうすもの。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:25.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니오. 사과할 쪽은 제 쪽입니다. 저는 야규 가(柳生家)의 주베라는 자.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:25.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,No. It's me who have to apologize. I am Jūbee of Yagyū Family(柳生家).
Comment: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:29.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,柳生家？っと言えば、将軍の親愛やく。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:29.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,야규 가? 그 말은 쇼군의 친애를 받는...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:29.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yagyū Family? Then you must be directly under the shōgun...
Comment: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:35.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,,将軍の命令でホーゾーインの様子を探るため、ムサシ殿を利用したのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:35.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쇼군의 명령으로 호조인의 모습을 정탐하기 위해 무사시 님을 이용했습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:35.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,I used you, Musashi, to spy upon Hōzōin, under the order of the shōgun.
Comment: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,この通り誤ります。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 이유로 사과드립니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's why I must apologize.
Comment: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:44.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや、おいらもジュウベエさんがいなかったら骨になっていたでござるだス。おいらこそありがとうだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:44.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니, 나도 주베 씨가 없었다면 뼈가 되어 있었을 것이오. 나야말로 고맙소.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:44.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, instead, if you wasn't there, Jūbee, I would end up as a skeleton-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. Thank you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:49.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ殿。その心の広さ、ジュウベエ関心しましたぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:49.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 님. 그 마음의 넓이, 이 주베가 감탄했습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:49.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi. I am struck with admiration for the breadth of your spirit!
Comment: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:51.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,,またまた調子いいだスから。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:51.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,또 또 약삭이 빠르기는!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:51.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're all talk again!
Comment: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:58.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,でも、一度ジュウベエ殿とお手合わせを願いたいでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:58.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도 다시 한번 주베 님과 승부를 부탁드리오.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:58.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,But still, I ask you for a match in the future once more-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それならばジパング武芸大会でお会いしましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다면 지팡구 무예대회에서 만납시다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then, we shall meet again in Jipangu Martial Arts Competition.
Comment: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:04.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,約束したでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:04.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,약속이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:04.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's a promise-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:07.13,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん。では、エドトピアで。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:07.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예. 그럼 에도토피아에서.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:07.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right. Then see you at Edotopia.
Comment: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:14.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,天下に名高いジュウベエとも知らず、師匠と呼ばれ、いい気分だったのもつかの間の夢。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:14.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,천하에 유명한 주베도 모르며 스승이라 불려 기분이 좋았던 것도 잠깐의 꿈.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:14.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Not knowing the world-famous Jūbee, he had a short but good dream, being called as a master.
Comment: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:22.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しかし、ホーゾーインといい勝負をしたムサシ、夢と希望に胸膨らませてエドトピアへと向かうのであった。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:22.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나, 호조인과 좋은 승부를 한 무사시. 꿈과 희망으로 가슴이 부풀어 에도토피아를 향하고 있었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:17.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Moreover, Musashi managed to have a good match against Hōzōin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:22.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,He was heading to Edotopia, heart rosen with dream and hope.
Comment: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵を待つのは花か嵐か。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시를 기다리는 자는 꽃인가 폭풍인가?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who will be waiting for Musashi? Wind or storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:43.90,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric01,カラのポケットに　ツキが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:47.15,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric02,飛び込むことも　あるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:49.53,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric03,おっきな声で　笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:52.16,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric04,あしたには　朝が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:57.50,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric05,無くすものなんか　何もないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:01.08,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric06,やっちゃえ！イケイケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:03.50,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric07,手ぶらは　強いぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:13.60,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric08,てなもんだ　のーてんきに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:21.65,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric09,人生　てなもんさ　チャンスが　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:26.36,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric10,しっぽを振って　追ってくるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:37.29,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric11,てなもんだ　のーてんきに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:45.75,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric12,未来も　てなもんさ　あしたが　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:51.59,SongED1,ref,0,0,0,ED1!Lyric13,両手ひろげて　笑ってるぜ
Comment: 0,0:24:04.62,0:24:06.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,一人旅ってのも結構疲れるもんだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.62,0:24:06.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,혼자 여행하는 것도 제법 힘든 것이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.62,0:24:06.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Being on a journey alone really is tiring-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:12.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,つい、うとうとしちまって、おいら、なんと刀を盗まれてしまっただス。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:12.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어느덧 꾸벅꾸벅 졸던 나는 이게 무슨, 칼을 도둑맞고 말았소.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:12.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,I was dozing, and what the?! My swords were stolen-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:16.50,Default,ja,0,0,0,,犯人を捜してるところへ、バイケンという男に出会うだスが、
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:16.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,범인을 찾던 곳에는 바이켄이라는 남자하고 만났지만
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:16.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,I met a man called Baiken while looking for the culprit,
Comment: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:19.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんと、犯人はその男の弟たちだったんだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:19.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알고 보니 범인은 그 남자의 형제들이었소.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:19.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,but the real culprit was actually his brothers.
Comment: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:24.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,次回！清く貧しいクサリガマだス。
